trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the workflow completes, the workflow runtime engine raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.WorkflowCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]當工作流程完成時，工作流程執行階段引擎引發<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.WorkflowCompleted>事件。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.WorkflowCompleted>

trans-unit.source: The workflow runtime engine passes all of the output parameters of the workflow in a WorkflowCompletedEventArgs.
trans-unit.target: 工作流程執行階段引擎會將所有的工作流程的輸出參數中 WorkflowCompletedEventArgs。

trans-unit.source: These include the `out` and `ref` parameters of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: 這些包括`out`和`ref`工作流程參數。

trans-unit.source: Gets the output from the workflow.
OutputParameters contains the `out` and `ref` parameters of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: 輸出參數包含`out`和`ref`工作流程參數。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> of values keyed by parameter name that contains the output parameters of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602>的值做為索引鍵所包含的工作流程的輸出參數的參數名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that represents the workflow definition on completion of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得<xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> ，代表完成工作流程執行個體的工作流程定義。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that represents the workflow definition on completion of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> ，代表完成工作流程執行個體的工作流程定義。
